        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2458450925" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15865184489894858151">This is the account of Paulo Coelho&apos;s spiritual journey along the Camino Santiago de Compostela, known in English as the Way of Saint James. It is a network of pilgrims&apos; ways serving pilgrimage to the shrine of the apostle Saint James the Great in the cathedral in Santiago Spain. Paulo is on this pilgrimage to gain insight and acceptance into the spiritual path he has chosen. He must do this to gain insight into the simplicity of life. The journey transforms him as he learns to understand the na</span>
  <span id="freeText15865184489894858151" style="display:none">This is the account of Paulo Coelho's spiritual journey along the Camino Santiago de Compostela, known in English as the Way of Saint James. It is a network of pilgrims' ways serving pilgrimage to the shrine of the apostle Saint James the Great in the cathedral in Santiago Spain. Paulo is on this pilgrimage to gain insight and acceptance into the spiritual path he has chosen. He must do this to gain insight into the simplicity of life. The journey transforms him as he learns to understand the nature of truth through the simplicity of life.<br />Many people have taken this journey over the centuries. Each having his own path to follow, his own lesson to learn. Each pilgrimage is different, each lesson is different.</span>
  <a data-text-id="15865184489894858151" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
